entries.next: You've been a big help. If I ever need more help, I won't hesitate to ask.
entries.cantwork: You've already got a job. Come see me when you need some work.
entries.npc_reset: If the job is too tough right now, see me soon and try again.
entries.npc_1_1: Hey there, friend, you have a friendly face. Perhaps you can help me with a little problem. I'm a spice trader, and I operate within the law -- mostly. But I was doing a little trading with the Lady Hutt's associates recently, and I think it might have been recorded. Can you help me?
entries.npc_2_1: Glad to hear it.  Some guy recorded my transaction and he's blackmailing me with it.  I want you to take care of him for me.  Can you do that?
entries.npc_3_1: It's just not my day, is it?
entries.npc_4_1: Right to the point. I like that. There's a guy who was hanging out near where I was talking to these, um...associates. I didn't notice him until my business was already concluded. I want you to take care of him. Will you do it?
entries.npc_backtowork_1: You haven't changed your mind about helping me, have you?
entries.npc_reward_1: That's top-flight work, friend. Thanks. Next time I'll be more careful about where I conduct my business.
entries.npc_work_1: Did you take out that blackmailer yet? I'm a nervous wreck here.
entries.npc_noloc_1: Give me a few minutes to get the exact coordinates. I'm a little jumpy today. In a little while I should have them.
entries.npc_failure_1: You couldn't take him down, eh? Well, thanks for trying.
entries.npc_breech_1: You're not getting this tape!  It's mine!  It'll make me rich!
entries.player_reset_1: I don't want this mission right now.
entries.player_sorry_1: I'll keep working on the mission.
entries.player_3_1: I'm not sure. What do you want me to do?
